This case-sensitive code system http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/measure-supplemental-data defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
age AgeAge Supplemental Data.
gender GenderGender Supplemental Data.
ethnicity EthnicityEthnicity Supplemental Data.
payer PayerPayer Supplemental Data.
race RaceRace Supplemental Data.

name: MeasureSupplementalData
title: MeasureSupplementalData
description: Identifier supplemental data in a population for measuring purposes.
